query:
UPDATE trips_detailed t
SET
    benchmark_weight_per_hour = q.benchmark_weight_per_hour,benchmark_weight_per_distance = q.benchmark_weight_per_distance,benchmark_fuel_consumption_liter = q.benchmark_fuel_consumption_liter,benchmark_weight_per_fuel_liter = q.benchmark_weight_per_fuel_liter,benchmark_catch_value_per_fuel_liter = q.benchmark_catch_value_per_fuel_liter,benchmark_eeoi = q.benchmark_eeoi,benchmark_status = q.benchmark_status,benchmark_state_counter = q.benchmark_state_counter
FROM (
    SELECT
        *
    FROM
        UNNEST (
            $1::BIGINT[],$2::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$3::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$4::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$5::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$6::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$7::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$8::INT[],$9::INT[]
        ) u (trip_id,benchmark_weight_per_hour,benchmark_weight_per_distance,benchmark_fuel_consumption_liter,benchmark_weight_per_fuel_liter,benchmark_catch_value_per_fuel_liter,benchmark_eeoi,benchmark_status,benchmark_state_counter)
) q
WHERE
    t.trip_id = q.trip_id AND (t.benchmark_state_counter = q.benchmark_state_counter)
